## 5. Related namespaces (same cluster)

| Namespace | Role |
|-----------|------|
| **vector-collector** | Another Vector deployment (often regional collectors forwarding to aggregator, or separate OTLP entry) |
| **jaeger** | Jaeger query/collector/agents — **OTLP on collector** (port **4317** on `jaeger-collector` LB in many setups); trace UI. *Check pod health — CrashLoop on one replica is a red flag in ops.* |
| **kafka** | **Strimzi** operator, **Kafka UI**, entity operator — event streaming next to observability pipelines |
| **ingress-nginx** | Ingress for UIs (Dashboards, etc.) |
| **cert-manager** | TLS certs for Ingress / sometimes internal |

